        <updateDate>2024-08-16T18:05:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>High Rise Fire Sprinkler Incentive Act of 2024</strong></p><p>This bill classifies any automatic&nbsp;fire sprinkler system retrofit property as 15-year property for purposes of accelerated depreciation using the straight line method.&nbsp;Such property is installed for use in residential property.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
